DESCRIPTION:OWN IT is an annual women and non-binary led wellness festival
  hosted on March 13th at the UC Davis Quad. The event will host a variety 
 of resources and activities to promote community building and retention. R
 esources include llamas and k-9 therapy dogs\, entertainment\, lawn games\
 , on-site accommodations\, workshops such as self-defense and pilates\, an
 d vendor and resource booths.
