SUMMARY:ARC Guitar Festival 2026
DESCRIPTION:The ARC Guitar Festival is returning to Winters on Saturday\, March 14 from 10am to 4pm at the Grand Ballroom at Hotel Winters! This event will feature handcrafted guitars built exclusively by the students of the ARC Guitar Building School. There will be guitar building demonstrations\, mini performances and lots of guitars to see and play. The best part is that it’s FREE – NO ADMISSION CHARGE! All ages are welcome! Experience functional art at its highest level.
