SUMMARY:Crux Crawford - Stand-up Comedy Show
DESCRIPTION:Watermelon Music is bringing the hilarious Crux Crawford to Davis\, CA on Saturday\, March 14th at 8pm! (Limited Seating) \nCrux Crawford is a nationally touring comedian with roots in Los Angeles. Known for his sharp\, relatable humor\, Crux’s material draws from his experiences as a father\, an aging millennial\, and the balancing act of managing family life while traveling the stand-up comedy circuit. \nWith millions of views on platforms like TikTok and YouTube\, Crux has quickly become a rising star in the comedy world. He’s shared the stage with comedy icons like Russell Peters\, Pablo Francisco\, Josh Blue\, and Pauly Shore\, among others. Crux was awarded Best of the Fest at the prestigious Burbank Comedy Festival\, solidifying his place as one of comedy’s most exciting up-and-comers. \n$20 in advance\, $30 at the door. \n18+ Only
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/crux-crawford-stand-up-comedy-show/
LOCATION:Melon Ball – Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, Suite #1\, Davis\, California\, 95616\, United States
