SUMMARY:Mosaics Beginning Spanish on Zoom
DESCRIPTION:Intercultural Mosaics\n**Discover Intercultural Mosaics This W
 inter 2025–2026!**\n\nJoin us for a vibrant and uplifting season of virt
 ual learning and community from **December 20\, 2025 to March 28\, 2026**
 —all from the comfort of your home on Zoom!\n\n**Zoom Link:** [https://z
 oom.us/j/589676463](https://zoom.us/j/589676463)\n\n**Bi-Weekly Friday Zoo
 m Sessions** *(Every 2nd and 4th Friday)*\n• **4:00 PM** – Advanced Ko
 rean with Stephen\n• **5:00 PM** – Intermediate Conversational Chinese
  with Sam\n• **6:00 PM** – Bible Study & Meditation Group with Stephen
 \n• **7:00 PM** – Beginning Chinese with Jane\n\n**Weekly Saturday Zoo
 m Sessions** (total of 12 sessions)\n• **4:00 PM** – Beginning Spanish
  with Viviana\n• **5:00 PM** – Beginning to Intermediate Korean with S
 tephen\n• **6:00 PM** – Beginning to Intermediate Japanese with Norio\
 n• **7:00 PM** – English Learners Group with Linda & Chad\n\n**Importa
 nt Notes:**\n\n1. **No Zoom sessions** on **January 2–3\, 2026** (New Ye
 ar) and **April 3–4\, 2026** (Easter).\n2. **Special Gatherings (Tentati
 ve):**\n**• February 14\, 2026:** Valentine’s Day & pre–Lunar New Ye
 ar celebration in person at Phoenix Hall\, 2nd Floor\, Davis Community Chu
 rch.\n**• March 14\, 2026:** Additional in-person gathering (tentative).
 \n\n**Return to In-Person Meetings:**\nWe will resume our **regular in-per
 son gatherings on April 11\, 2026** at the **2nd floor rooms of Phoenix Ha
 ll\, Davis Community Church**.\n\nFor more information about Intercultural
  Mosaics classes and activities\, visit **[www.nextg.org](http://www.nextg
 .org)** or contact **Dr. Stephen Moon** at **916-217-5470** or **catalyst@
 nextg.org**.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mosaics/events/313594928/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T011426Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T011426Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
