DESCRIPTION:Join us for a lap-sit program for babies ages 0 to 18 months a
 nd their caregivers followed by a Stay-and-Play. We will share songs\, lul
 labies\, fingerplays\, and board books!\n\nThe program is held indoors\, 
 in the Blanchard Room and is offered in two-month sessions. Each session i
 s limited to 30 families.\n\nThis program is offered by registration only
 . In addition\, all babies must have a Yolo County library account.\n\n
 The March / April Session has two spots left. If interested\, please regis
 ter at this link.
