UID:10002793-1774630800-1774641600@visitdavis.org
SUMMARY:Friday-Fest
DESCRIPTION:🎷🍕 Friday-Fest at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis 🍷🎶\nFriday\, March 27 | 5–8 PM \nLive Music Friday’s are back! Join us for Friday-Fest\, featuring live jazz from the Potential Jazz Ensemble and fresh\, wood-fired pizza from Italian Brother’s Pizza. Your ticket includes a glass of wine and live music—the perfect pairing. \n🍕 Food starts at 5 PM with authentic\, made-to-order pizzas hot from the wood-fired oven.\n🎶 Live music from 6–7:30 PM\, with the Potential Jazz Ensemble bringing vibrant\, feel-good jazz that blends classic roots with modern creativity. Expect smooth grooves\, lively solos\, and great energy from this talented lineup of sax\, bass\, guitar\, piano\, and percussion. \nCome early\, grab a slice\, sip some wine\, and settle in for a relaxed\, delicious evening at the vineyard. Weekend vibes start here! 🍷✨
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/friday-fest/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Highway128PressTrip_GreatBearVineyards_2024_MaxWhittaker_12-Copy-scaled-OoIRnT.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
