DESCRIPTION:On March 28th\, we will rise up\, take to the streets\, and sa
 y it loud: No Thrones! No Crowns! No Kings! We’re not watching history h
 appen—we’re making it. Yolo residents from across the county will gath
 er together at beautiful RiverWalk Park in West Sacramento to fight for ou
 r democracy. At 11:30 there will be a brief program before we march en mas
 se at noon across the majestic Tower Bridge to the State Capitol where we 
 join with other groups coming from across the Sacramento area. The preside
 nt 
