UID:c50db143265617aaabeebbd74ab1c2e6332026_7:22:51_PM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:UC Davis has 11 student-run clinics that all help provide care
  to underserved communities in the Sacramento area. Patients and volunteer
 s often run into similiar issues\, yet there is little opportunity to coll
 aborate with one another. This seminar aims to increase connections betwee
 n volunteers at our student-run clinics for our patients and our students'
  wellbeing. Occuring for the third year in a row\, we hope to maintain and
  grow ties between all the patient-serving communities at UC Davis.
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=908453
X-SOURCE:UC Davis CampusGroups
