DESCRIPTION:Fundraiser\n\nJoin us for an exciting afternoon hosted by have
 n a boutique at Morgan's Mill in Woodland\, for our Runway of Hope Fashion
  Show fundraiser benefiting Yolo County CASA (Court Appointed Special Advo
 cates). Models will showcase the latest summer fashion\, and you'll receiv
 e an amazing swag bag filled with goodies. Enjoy appetizers\, along with c
 omplimentary wine and beer\, while you decide which silent auction item yo
 u'd like to take home. And wear your most fabulous hat or fascinator to wi
 n prizes during the show! All proceeds go toward Yolo CASA's program to re
 cruit\, train\, and support our volunteers who change lives by working one
 -on-one with youth in foster care. Generously sponsored by Yolo Eats and h
 aven a boutique.
LOCATION:Morganâs Mill\, Woodland\, Woodland\, CA 95695
