DESCRIPTION:Join the WSAC Visibility Brigade each Friday afternoon at 4:30
  to make VISIBLE our opposition to the endless corruption\, incompetence\,
  and immorality of the current regime. We display messages to commuters th
 at aim to ACTIVATE\, WAKE-UP\, and EMPATHIZE. Hundreds of people will see 
 our messages in 60 minutes! We have a lot of fun and receive hundreds of h
 onks\, thumbs up\, and power fists. All you have to do it show up and wave
 ! Details provided upon registration. Look for the email you receive after
LOCATION:West Sacramento\, CA
