SUMMARY:Mosaics Acoustic Guitar & Singing Group
DESCRIPTION:Davis Art\, Music & Outdoor Activities Meetup\n**Discover Inte
 rcultural Mosaics This Winter 2025–2026!**\n\nJoin us for a vibrant and 
 uplifting season of virtual learning and community from **December 20\, 20
 25 to March 28\, 2026**—all from the comfort of your home on Zoom!\n\n**
 Registration is required\, and the Zoom link will be provided exclusively 
 to those who sign up.**\n\n**Bi-Weekly Friday Zoom Sessions** *(Every 2nd 
 and 4th Friday)*\n• **4:00 PM** – Advanced Korean with Stephen\n• **
 5:00 PM** – Intermediate Conversational Chinese with Sam\n• **6:00 PM*
 * – Bible Study & Meditation Group with Stephen\n• **7:00 PM** – Beg
 inning Chinese with Jane\n\n**Weekly Saturday Zoom Sessions** (total of 12
  sessions)\n• **4:00 PM** – Beginning Spanish with Viviana\n• **5:00
  PM** – Beginning to Intermediate Korean with Stephen\n• **6:00 PM** 
 – Beginning to Intermediate Japanese with Norio\n• **7:00 PM** – Eng
 lish Learners Group with Linda & Chad\n\n**Important Notes:**\n\n1. **No Z
 oom sessions** on **January 2–3\, 2026** (New Year) and **April 3–4\, 
 2026** (Easter).\n2. **Special Gatherings (Tentative):**\n**• February 1
 4\, 2026:** Valentine’s Day & pre–Lunar New Year celebration in person
  at Phoenix Hall\, 2nd Floor\, Davis Community Church.\n**• March 14\, 2
 026:** Additional in-person gathering (tentative).\n\n**Return to In-Perso
 n Meetings:**\nWe will resume our **regular in-person gatherings on April 
 11\, 2026** at the **2nd floor rooms of Phoenix Hall\, Davis Community Chu
 rch**.\n\nFor more information about Intercultural Mosaics classes and act
 ivities\, visit **[www.nextg.org](http://www.nextg.org)** or contact **Dr.
  Stephen Moon** at **916-217-5470** or **catalyst@nextg.org**.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/intercultural-mosaics/events/xgkgvtyj
 cgbhc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251215T211410Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251215T211410Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
