SUMMARY:PRIDE Tabling Event
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260512T210000
UID:132065d370b512ae7d699452c7e4d4fc3132026_1:24:26_PM@campusgroups.com
DESCRIPTION:Join the Center for Student Involvement (CSI) for a vibrant Pr
 ide Month tabling event at UC Davis! Registered Student Organizations (RSO
 s) are invited to sign up for a table\, showcase their work\, fundraise fo
 r their causes\, and connect with the UC Davis community.\nCome enjoy the 
 lively atmosphere\, meet amazing student orgs\, show your Pride spirit\, a
 nd be part of a supportive\, joyful celebration of LGBTQIA+ identities on 
 campus. Whether you're tabling or just stopping by\, everyone is welcome t
 o join the fun!
URL:https://aggielife.ucdavis.edu/rsvp?id=908478
